snippet.textDisplay:
Before I knew BTS, I was LOST and I had NO MORE DREAM. I gave up and begged for someone to SAVE ME. I told them IM FINE, but I prayed for help. I was in DANGER. I tried to RUN and I screamed silently ‘I NEED YOU’. I wanted a BUTTERFLY feeling in my stomach. I wanted a GOOD DAY. When I found BTS, everything changed. They were able to MAKE IT RIGHT. They became my IDOL. They were my FRIENDS and they helped my MOON turn to a sun! They stopped the SHADOW holding me down! My EGO grew because of them! They helped me get through the pain from my BLOOD, SWEAT & TEARS that I’ve shed in the past. They helped me realise that NO, I shouldn’t doubt myself. In fact, I should LOVE MYSELF and view the MAP OF THE SOUL in order to find who I truly am. They helped me find the confidence to confess to my MISS RIGHT! They became part of my DNA. They brought out the BEST OF ME. I found that in order to find my true PERSONA, I have to take the pain head ON. But there were times when BTS were close to an end. I begged them; DON’T LEAVE ME! And they stayed! The SPRING DAY became my favourite day of the year. I may still experience some hints of FAKE LOVE but SO WHAT? The BLACK SWAN is no longer existent in my world! I still struggle, but BTS have taken me into a MAGIC SHOP and helped me find my HOME.

MIC DROP.
